{"tid":1809612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全民口罩日乘勢而起","createTime":"2020-01-03T08:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T19:00:12.000Z","uid":116074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8978acaa93a828a18f51797fe87c1e746cf7b274","tid":1809612,"uid":116074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:33:54.000Z","msg":"事源： 大家都覺得帶口罩，係一個抗爭嘅意識形態嘅表現但係全民口罩日從來都好似冇「起」勢。<br />\n<br />\n所以我一直諗，彩色pitta masl比起黑色pitta mask，會唔會更加有吸引力呢，作為一個時尚打扮嘢副作用。<br />\np.s. 我覺得戴綠色pitta mask嘅人係幾型<br />\n<br />\n可惜嘅係，一路都冇一個「天時」，去令全民口罩日盛行。但可能香港命不該絕，武漢事件造就了「天時」。<br />\n<br />\n在此，我建議<strong>擔心</strong>嘅人就梗係要戴口罩出街喇！<br />\n而<strong>唔擔心</strong>嘅人都可以帶不同顏色pitta mask扮自己驚，同時又有打扮嘅作用，一石二鳥！<br />\n<br />\n祝 願全民口罩日迅速成風。 Comment如果有賣唔同顏色pitta mask嘅黃店既地址！"},{"pid":"aed1c030acee8e52b213e7d4886c1584a7483050","tid":1809612,"uid":282490,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"咁無大志<br />\n係都推全民豬咀日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3752041fcf3ca3e03568b9ee475a71f010ffead4","tid":1809612,"uid":247892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:46:42.000Z","msg":"齊齊幪面吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac59fa445219b31f53de19db729bb0bdca406153","tid":1809612,"uid":333013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:50:05.000Z","msg":"以後遊行，希望我嗌以下口號嘅時候，可以一呼百應！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前 線 好 珍 貴<br />\n唔 好 再 捉 鬼</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Credit: pepe上PE 巴打</strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"c95c4e9922ee07b0060f80979107e4a9752db3c7","tid":1809612,"uid":8732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:24:06.000Z","msg":"[突發] 黃色